* One is run by Redaktion Buergerwelle at http://groups.yahoo.com/group/emf-omega-news/

* another one is EMR Updates, run by Art Kab and also published through a Yahoo group: http://health.groups.yahoo.com/group/emfrefugee/

Some more details on electromagnetic waves affecting trees are here

